            ></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <section data-bright>
        <NextEvent client:only="react" />
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="inner-section">
          <h2>About Paderborn.js</h2>
          <div>
            <p>
              Paderborn.js meets regularly at <a
                href="https://enpit.de/"
                rel="noopener">Enpit</a
              > in Paderborn.
            </p>
            <p>
              We welcome a diverse range of topics that are related JavaScript
              software engineering. Sometimes we host talks, sometimes it's just
              a get together to socialice between like-minded individuals,
              getting to know each other.
            </p>
            <p>
              If you have an idea about a talk or topic you aren’t sure about,
              just reach out or add it as an issue in our Paderborn.js <a
                href="https://github.com/paderbornjs/talks"
                color="blue">talks repository</a
              >!
            </p>
            <p>
              Join the <a href="https://meetup.com/paderborn-js" color="blue"
                >Meetup group</a
              > to get in contact with the community and sign up to our events.
            </p>
            <p>
              We look forward to hearing from you, and to seeing you at an
              upcoming event!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section data-bright>
        <div class="inner-section">
          <h2>The team</h2>
          <div class="team">
            <div>
              <h3>Janis</h3><img src="janis.jpg" /><p>
                Software Developer at <a href="https://enpit.de" rel="noopener"
                  >enpit</a
                >. Likes to solve scaling and performance problems when
                bouldering.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Christoph</h3><img src="christoph.jpg" /><p>
                Director UI Engineering at <a
                  href="https://smartclip.tv"
                  rel="noopener">smartclip</a
                >. Open source contributor and maintainer, blogs at <a
                  href="https://codepunkt.de"
                  rel="noopener">Codepunkt</a
                >.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="inner-section">
          <h2>Code of Conduct</h2>
          <div>
            <p>
              This meetup’s primary goal is to have an awesome, inclusive and
              safe community meetup where people meet, hang out together, chat,
              listen to talks, exchange ideas and make new friends.
            </p>
            <p>
              We invite all those who participate in our events to help us
              create a safe and positive experience for everyone. Any harmful or
              discriminating behaviour will not be tolerated. We reserve the
              right to exclude people from the events.
            </p>
            <p>
              For details on what kinds of behaviour are not tolerated and
              consequences for violating these rules, we refer to the <a
                href="http://berlincodeofconduct.org/"
                color="blue">Berlin Code of Conduct</a
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section data-bright>
        <div class="inner-section sponsors">
          <h2>Sponsors</h2>
          <div>
            <a href="https://enpit.de" rel="noopener"><img src="enpit.svg" /></a>
            <div>
              Enpit hosts our events right in the center of Paderborn and pays
              for our Meetup group!
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  html {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI',
      Roboto, 'Noto Sans', Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial,
      sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    color: rgb(0, 36, 102);
    background: rgb(235, 241, 244);
    line-height: 1.625;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 550px) {
    body {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    body {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  h1 svg {
    margin: 24px;
    max-width: 100%;
    height: 64px;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  h1 .wordmark path {
    fill: #25546b;
  }
  h1 .logomark path {
    fill: none;
    stroke: black;
    stroke-width: 4;
  }
  @keyframes j {
    0% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 881;
    }
    29% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
    30% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    }
    60% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    }
    100% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    }
  }
  @keyframes s {
    0% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 1241;
    }
    29% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 1241;
    }
    59% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
    60% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    }
    100% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      fill: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    }
  }
  h1 .logomark path:nth-of-type(1) {
    stroke-dasharray: 881;
    stroke-dashoffset: 881;
    animation: j 2s linear 1s forwards;
  }
  h1 .logomark path:nth-of-type(2) {
    stroke-dasharray: 1241;
    stroke-dashoffset: 1241;
    animation: s 2s linear 1s forwards;
  }

  section[data-bright] {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .team {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .team h3 {
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .team img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 250px;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
  }

  .team p {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 550px) {
    h1 {
      margin: 12px 0;
    }
    h1 svg {
      height: 96px;
    }
    .team {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .team > div {
      width: 50%;
    }
    .team img {
      width: 200px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      margin: 24px 0 12px 0;
    }
    h1 svg {
      height: 128px;
    }
    .team {
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .team img {
      width: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>

<style is:global>
  a,
  a:link,
  a:visited {
    color: #2665d9;
  }

  a:focus,
  a:hover,
  a:active {
    color: #009a00;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0px 0px 16px;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.4em;
  }

  h2 em {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: normal;
    background: #fffacc;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .inner-section {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .sponsors > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .sponsors img {
    min-height: 150px;
    margin-right: 24px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 550px) {
    .inner-section {
      padding: 36px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8em;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    .inner-section {
      padding: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
